name: CAN.OBJ.2021/12
description:
CAN.OBJ.2021/12 captures a year of activity on CreativeApplications.Net, represented as a cube with every article, category greyscale, and ‘spike’ according to traffic in 2021. 

— 4512 articles (2008-2021) = 6378 data points
— Light/Dark = Article category by volume
— Height = View count in 2021

1280x1280px / mp4 / 512 frames / 17sec loop
